# SSH private key removed from version control.
# 
# To use this project, provide the required SSH private key via a secure
# mechanism such as:
#   - environment variables
#   - a secret management tool (e.g., Vault, cloud secret manager)
#   - SSH agent forwarding
#   - a private key file stored outside of the repository
#
# IMPORTANT:
# - Never commit private keys to version control
# - Revoke and rotate any SSH keys that were previously stored here.
# - Rewrite Git history to remove the old key material from all commits.
